\f1\i\b \cf0 #### The Kinsey Report
\f0\i0\b0 \

\f1\i\b \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\partightenfactor0

\f2\i0\b0 \cf0 `\\index[gamebook]\{Kinsey Report|(\}`\{=latex\}In 1948, `\\index[gamebook]\{Kinsey, Alfred\}`\{=latex\}Alfred C. Kinsey (b. 1894 \'96 d. August 25, 1956) published
\f3\i  *Sexual Behavior in the Human Male*
\f2\i0 . It was revolutionary.
\f0 \

\f2 \
Kinsey and his assistants had interviewed 5,300 white males from all walks of American life. The interviews required up to 521 questions, depending on the interviewee\'92s experiences.  Kinsey reported that a large number of men\'97up to 45%\'97reported having at least one homosexual encounter during his adolescence.  These encounters are most frequent at young age, dropping to a stable 10% of the population by age 20-25. These numbers, Kinsey fears, may not tell the whole story because:
\f0 \

\f2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li283\partightenfactor0
\cf0 >The social significance of the homosexual is considerably emphasized by the fact that both Jewish and Christian churches have considered this aspect of human sexuality to be abnormal and immoral. \'85 Social custom and our Anglo-American law are sometimes very severe in penalizing one who is discovered to have had homosexual relations. In consequence, many persons who have had such experiences are psychically disturbed, and not a few of them have been in open conflict with the social organization. ([p. 610][#Kinsey:1998ur])
\f0 \

\f2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The Kinsey report found that homosexual activity as a common part of male sexual development.  Self-identifying as a homosexual, or engaging exclusively in homosexual activity, was found to be more rare. But at 10%, it was almost twice as high as any previous scientific {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://B871DADE-52D7-40F0-A501-E43B1D15848C"}}{\fldrslt estimate}}. Almost as importantly, Kinsey identified the source of psychic disturbance
\f3\i  *not*
\f2\i0  to be the homosexual activity itself, but the social structures that penalize such behavior.`\\index[gamebook]\{Kinsey Report|)\}`\{=latex\}
\f0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sb240\sa120\partightenfactor0

