\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li283\fi-283\partightenfactor0
\cf0 `\\index[gamebook]\{Stonewall|(\}`\{=latex\}By the 1960s, tensions were growing in the gay community. Another group of younger {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://76550411-8600-49F2-B901-57086044E599"}}{\fldrslt gay}} activists were growing irritated with both the slow progress of the Mattachine society and its restrictions on behavior. In 1968, a group of young 'street-activists' disrupted a meeting of the American Medical Association in New York by shouting down Charles Socarides, a Psychiatrist known for his psychoanalytic treatment of homosexuals.
\fs24 `\\index[gamebook]\{Socarides, Charles\}`\{=latex\}
\f0 \

\f2\fs20 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\partightenfactor0

